item.title: Astronaught
item.dc:creator: zeok
item.description: Astronaught is a Exploration Tower Defense game where you gather resources during the day and upgrade your ship to fight enemies in the night. The objective in the game is to survive as long as possible.
item.content:encoded:
Summary

  • Spawning system for resources and buildings
  • Ship refuelling mechanic
  • Jetpack Ability
  • Resource Areas
  • Buildings

Astronaught is a Exploration Tower Defense game where you gather resources during the day and upgrade your ship to fight enemies in the night. The objective in the game is to survive as long as possible.
